@Versace last night!
Big love always to @donatella_versace and the whole team!! 🖤 @pg_dmcasting @kjeldgaard1 @gregswalesart

@MOSCHINO is the MOST FUN POSSIBLE way to end a day! @itsjeremyscott let(s) them eat cake - & WHATEVER THE F ELSE THEY WANT 🍰‼️ Love you so much my sweet J and @carlynecerfdedudzeele 💞💞💐🍦🍧🥮🍡🍮 Thank you for all the wonderlands you teleport us to 🏰

Every opportunity to walk a @prada show is a blessing ❣️ So much gratitude to Mrs. Prada, @olivierizzo, @ashleybrokaw, @zambishot, @la_vanin and everyone else behind the scenes !! Quality, quality, quality- today & always. 🚨⛽️

It’s a dream come true to be on the cover of @i_d !! 💚🍓🥕 HUGE THANKS to @alastairmckimm @jamie.hawkesworth @olivierizzo @samuel_ellis && appreciate the interview (live from the farm!) by @jacksunnucks / link in bio 🍃
Karl ❤️ we miss you so much! ☁️

Me n my sweet sis @bellahadid for @voguemagazine’s March issue ! 🧡 thanks angels @mr_carlos_nazario @studio_jackson BIG LOVE always

There are some shows that you wish you could walk and be in the audience for at the same time !!❣️The energy (& guests’ faces!) in this room was unforgettable. I love you @themarcjacobs thank you for including me in another of your one-of-a-kind visions !!!! Forever a great honor and pleasure @kegrand @bitton CONGRATULATIONS to the entire @marcjacobs team ❤️

Was so happy and grateful to walk @proenzaschouler last night and finally work with the sweetest coolest cats (and fellow @thenewschool alum;)) - Jack & Lazaro !! thank you so much for having me & for this killer look !!! @ashleybrokaw ❣️

Not only are Mary-Kate and Ashley two of my forever style icons, but I also look up to them for their ability to transcend each creative world they’ve taken on based on talent, work ethic, humbleness, kindness, and staying true to themselves. It was an honor and pleasure to open this show and be part of their vision- continuously tempted to fill my whole closet with @therow !!! Thank you @emperor.lee @nianfish and the whole team for the sweetest morning ♡

Last night- @TOMFORD’s West Coast ! 🥂✨🌙
Thank you forever and always Tom and @carineroitfeld- I will never forget your support from the beginning, and it will never stop being an honor!! 🖤 @pg_dmcasting #TOMFORDAW20

NEW @maxmara with my badass amazing sisters @adrianalima @joansmalls @irinashayk - the best day, by two of the all-time greatest #StevenMeisel & @carineroitfeld 💙💗💜💚 thanks so much @ian_griffiths1 @pg_dmcasting and the whole MM team x
I LOVE THIS COLLECTION !!!!

happiest birthday to yooouuu @livvperez 🧁 as we head into another quarter-century of friendship and sisterhood !!! Proud & impressed by all you continue to juggle and accomplish - always with style, class, intelligence, curiosity, determination, and sweetness ! 🌼 YOU ARE SO LOVED. Wishing you the best year :)

This is too much. Rest In Peace and love together, legends. Growing up a Kobe fan brought so much joy to my life, like so many, and we were all so excited to see sweet Gigi play someday. Sending strength and my deepest condolences to Vanessa, the Bryant family, and all the families affected by this tragedy.

JPG was the first designer to welcome me onto a Paris runway, for his last ready-to-wear collection in 2014. Last night, all that gathered to celebrate his 50 YEARS & final Couture collection was a testament to what a worldwide icon and inspiration he is !!! I am so honored to have been a small part in your legendary creative vision @jpgaultierofficial THANK YOU for your warmth, spirit, and all the life and art you have shared with us. 💙
